  ('locality-f29af906-moex-00008', 'locality-f29af906', 'locality-f29af906-moex-114-d3e6a6cd', 'sub-locality-f29af906-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲為從事採取、加工、販售砂石業務之業者，因有部分不法盜採之嫌，
